channel.title: 508 Source + Client
channel.description: Alright, so every source and client I have found either the links are broken or there is no cache and I cannot find it anywhere. I was wondering if anyone has a NON PVP/SPAWN server that does not have any customs. Like a blank server but.. not really. I've tried downloading a blank but the links were broken and it was 308. I want a 308 loading 508 cache or just a 508/525. I don't care if its PI/Delta or InsidiaX/etc. I'm taring it down and re-coding just about everything. Thanks. :)
